{
  "texts": [
    "Then, the image divides into nine sub-regions, each encoded by the Image Encoder.",
    "Image features for each sub-region calculate similarity with the encoded text to obtain the most similar text features.",
    "Then, the most similar text features, global image features, and local features concatenate together.",
    "Finally, the concatenated features input into the WGA-PoolFormer captioning model to generate corresponding image captions.",
    "The methods mentioned above are shown in Figure 2, the TSIC-CLIP image captioning model."
  ]
}